 Representative Cases

$18.4 million verdict obtained for individual client in breach of contract and fraud lawsuit arising out of sale of oilfield services company  (tried in Grayson County, Texas).

Defense verdict for hospital in wrongful death case arising out of knee replacement surgery (tried in Gallatin County, Montana)

 Defense verdict for clinic in wrongful birth case involving cystic fibrosis (tried in Gallatin County, Montana)

 Defense verdict for lawyer and AmLaw 100 law firm in multi-million dollar legal malpractice lawsuit alleging negligence, gross negligence and breach of fiduciary duty.

 Defense verdict for major north Texas hospital in $30 million lawsuit alleging actual and punitive damages for conspiracy, defamation and tortious interference with existing and prospective contracts.

 Defense verdict for major north Texas hospital in $40 million lawsuit alleging infant’s cerebral palsy was caused by preventable birth asphyxia (tried in the United States District court for the Eastern District of Texas, Marshall division for a Dallas-based hospital).

 Defense verdict for major west Texas hospital in $30 million lawsuit alleging infant’s cerebral palsy was caused by preventable birth asphyxia.

 Defense verdict for major south Texas hospital in $30 million lawsuit alleging infant’s cerebral palsy was caused by preventable birth asphyxia.
  
 Defense verdict for major north Texas hospital in $25 million lawsuit alleging infant’s cerebral palsy was caused by preventable birth asphyxia.

 Defense verdict for major north Texas hospital in $10 million lawsuit alleging profound and permanent brain damage to adult patient resulting from allegedly preventable post-operative complications (Following the defense verdict, we successfully challenged through the Supreme Court of Texas the trial court’s grant of a new trial, overturning more than 100 years of precedent allowing trial judges to grant new trials for no reason at all).

 Defense verdict for thoracic surgeon in $10 million lawsuit brought by plaintiff fellow thoracic surgeon for permanent and profound debilitating injury sustained as a result of allegedly negligent surgery. 

 Complete dismissal of lawyer and law firm in multi-million dollar legal malpractice lawsuit during trial. 

 Defense verdict for major north Texas hospital in wrongful death case alleging nursing malpractice. 

 Defense verdict for surgeon in wrongful death case alleging surgeon malpractice.

 Defense verdict for thoracic surgeon in transfusion-associated AIDS wrongful death malpractice case. 

 Defense verdict for north Texas certified registered nurse anesthetist in wrongful death lawsuit alleging nurse anesthesia malpractice. 

 Defense verdict for addiction medicine specialist in wrongful death lawsuit alleging malpractice resulting in suicide.
  
 Defense verdict for emergency room physician in lawsuit alleging profound and permanent injury resulting from alleged malpractice. 

 Defense verdict for west Texas certified registered nurse anesthetist and his group in wrongful death lawsuit alleging nurse anesthesia malpractice.

 Defense verdict for surgeon in lawsuit alleging profound and permanent injury resulting from alleged surgical malpractice.

 Defense verdict for small town family practice physician in lawsuit alleging profound and permanent injury resulting from alleged malpractice. 

 National trial counsel for catastrophic loss and birth injury lawsuits for several hospital systems and insurance carriers. 

 Summary judgment in favor of health maintenance organization in $100 million class action for breach of fiduciary duty (affirmed on appeal).

 Representation of the nation’s largest health maintenance organization in numerous complex claims and proceedings arising out of the alleged mismanagement of a kidney transplant program. 

 Representation of numerous health maintenance organizations and associated physician groups in medical malpractice and managed care lawsuits.
  
 Coordinating counsel for managed care litigation for the nations’ largest health maintenance organization. 

 Representation of member organization before the United Network of Organ Sharing. 

 Representation of pharmaceutical products company in federal and state courts in Texas, Alabama, Illinois, New York and California in products liability claims and lawsuits alleging wrongful deaths and permanent and profound injuries to minors. 

 Representation of a major pharmaceutical company in numerous premises liability toxic tort lawsuits.

 Representation of major cancer treatment center in numerous wrongful death and other lawsuits of alleged malpractice. 

 Representation of numerous privately held companies and an individual in a $50 million action for breach of fiduciary, breach of contract and conspiracy. 

 Representation of attorney in lawsuit alleging conspiracy arising out of involvement with federal income tax informant. 

 Representation of physicians and nurses before state licensing boards. 

 Representation of federal governmental entities in director and officer investigations, claims and litigation arising out of savings and loan and bank failures. 

 Representation of design engineering company in numerous claims and lawsuits alleging engineering malpractice. 

 Representation of cryogenic laboratory in lawsuit alleging permanent and profound injuries to newborn arising out of alleged product defect and malpractice. 

 Representation of major hospital in breach of contract action arising out of professional services. 

 Representation of product manufacturer and distributor in lawsuit alleging wrongful termination, conspiracy and age discrimination. 

 Representation of lawyer and law firm in lawsuit alleging conspiracy and theft of trade secrets. 

 Representation of personal watercraft owner in wrongful death action alleging negligent entrustment. 

 Representation of large hospital system in lawsuit brought by anesthesiologist alleging anti-trust, conspiracy and tortious interference with existing and prospective contracts. 

 Representation of large hospital in lawsuit brought by cardiothoracic surgeon alleging defamation, breach of contract, tortious interference and conspiracy. 

 Representation of franchisee in lawsuit alleging negligent hiring of convicted felon. 

 Representation of school district administrators in employment actions.

